                        { question: 'In how many ways can a team of 11 be chosen from 15 players?', solution: 'Order does not matter. \\({}^{15}C_{11} = {}^{15}C_{4} = (15\\times14\\times13\\times12)/(4\\times3\\times2\\times1) = 1365\\).' }
